  "texts": [
    "To sum up, Pritchard's solution to the technology-education tension is affected by at least four problems.",
    "First, the conditions for EXT are not clear.",
    "Second, even if they are clarified in theory, they may not be easily recognizable in practice.",
    "Third, even if they will be clarified and easily recognizable, they may not apply to every form of tool-use and to every TET case.",
    "Fourth, cognitive tool-uses, whether they can be considered as EMB or EXT, may have different kinds of effects on different components of the cognitive character of students, 6 some of which may be detrimental."
  ],
